description:
Trunk Club is a personal shopping service for premium men's clothing. After getting started, you'll be contacted by a real human being on our team for a short consultation. Your stylist will hand-select items from our curated inventory and ship them to your door. Try everything on at home and send back any unwanted items. Pay only for items you keep -- there are no extra fees/commitments.

Example prices for items we'll send you: Jeans ($160-$200), Dress Shirts ($100-$200), Sweaters ($90-$150)

Trunk Club features:
• Premium brands, handpicked and shipped to you by a real person
• Prices on par with high-end department stores or boutiques
• Pay only for items you keep
• Free shipping, both ways
• No monthly commitments or membership fees

Exclusive iOS features:
• Request a "trunk" personalized to just what you need, from wherever you are. Your stylist is just a tap away.
• View past purchases in your wardrobe and receive outfit recommendations from your stylist
• Browse exclusive featured brands and styles curated by our merchandising team. One tap notifies your stylist that you're interested.

If you have questions or feedback, we'd love to hear from you at iphone@trunkclub.com.
releaseNotes: We just realized there's no consensus for release names here at Trunk Club. Three dot four? Three point four? Three dash four? Three four? Crazy, right?! So what does this have to do with the latest release? Nothing. It's placeholder copy because the bugs we fixed aren't worth mentioning or are too complicated to explain.
